description: Looking for an “Upscale” Southern-style BBQ experience? The Porketeers  Catering brings the traditional and wholly unique experience of Southern-style Pit Bar-B-Que to the Southern California area. We bring our customers delicious smoked specialty meats and elegant side dishes typically found served at regional feasts.Bringing a well-loved Southern tradition to your event our grill caterers specialize in serving slow, wood-smoked Pit BBQ meats.
name: Porketeers
